    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div id="music163player"><br>    <iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=28815250&auto=1&height=66"></iframe><br>  </div><p>常用命令</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new &quot;postName&quot; #新建文章</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate #生成静态页面至public目录</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean #清除缓存</span><br><span class="line">hexo server #开启预览访问端口（默认端口4000，&apos;ctrl + c&apos;关闭server）</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy #部署到GitHub</span><br><span class="line">hexo help  # 查看帮助</span><br><span class="line">hexo version  #查看Hexo的版本</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">缩写</span><br><span class="line">hexo n == hexo new</span><br><span class="line">hexo g == hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo s == hexo server</span><br><span class="line">hexo d == hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">组合命令</span><br><span class="line">hexo s -g #生成并本地预览</span><br><span class="line">hexo d -g #生成并上传</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>博客备份<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">将仓库clone到本地 bai.github.io</span><br><span class="line">_config.yml，themes/，source，scffolds/，package.json，.gitignore</span><br><span class="line">复制到你克隆下来的仓库文件夹</span><br><span class="line">将themes/next/中的.git/删除，否则无法将主题文件夹push</span><br><span class="line">在bai.github.io文件夹下打开git bash 执行npm install，npm install hexo-deployer-git 确定分支是否为上传分支</span><br><span class="line">执行git add .，git commit -m &quot;提交文件&quot;，git push origin master来提交,如果提交默认分支git push master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title:  # 这是标题</span><br><span class="line">categories:  # 这里写的分类会自动汇集到 categories 页面上，分类可以多级</span><br><span class="line">- 实用技术 # 一级分类</span><br><span class="line">- 个人博客 # 二级分类</span><br><span class="line">tags:   # 这里写的标签会自动汇集到 tags 页面上</span><br><span class="line">- 实用 # 可配置多个标签，注意格式</span><br><span class="line">- 个人博客</span><br><span class="line">description: #博客的详细介绍</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font color="#FF0000"> 我可以设置这一句的颜色哈哈 </font></p><p><font size="6"> 我还可以设置这一句的大小嘻嘻 </font></p><p><font size="5" color="#FF0000"> 我甚至可以设置这一句的颜色和大小呵呵</font></p><p><center>居中它</center><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font color=&quot;#FF0000&quot;&gt; 我可以设置这一句的颜色哈哈 &lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font size=6&gt; 我还可以设置这一句的大小嘻嘻 &lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font size=5 color=&quot;#FF0000&quot;&gt; 我甚至可以设置这一句的颜色和大小呵呵&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;center&gt;居中它&lt;/center&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>表格</p><table><thead><tr><th>Tables</th><th style="text-align:center">Are</th><th style="text-align:right">Cool</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>col 1 is</td><td style="text-align:center">left-aligned</td><td style="text-align:right">$1600</td></tr><tr><td>col 2 is</td><td style="text-align:center">centered</td><td style="text-align:right">$12</td></tr><tr><td>col 3 is</td><td style="text-align:center">right-aligned</td><td style="text-align:right">$1</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">创建表格和其他文字留出一行空格</span><br><span class="line">| Tables   |      Are      |  Cool |</span><br><span class="line">|----------|:-------------:|------:|</span><br><span class="line">| col 1 is |  left-aligned | $1600 |</span><br><span class="line">| col 2 is |    centered   |   $12 |</span><br><span class="line">| col 3 is | right-aligned |    $1 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://hexo.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">超链接</a><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[超链接](https://hexo.io/)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h1 id="一级标题-最大字号"><a href="#一级标题-最大字号" class="headerlink" title="一级标题(最大字号)"></a>一级标题(最大字号)</h1><h2 id="二级标题-比一级标题小一号"><a href="#二级标题-比一级标题小一号" class="headerlink" title="二级标题(比一级标题小一号)"></a>二级标题(比一级标题小一号)</h2><h3 id="三级标题-比二级标题小一号"><a href="#三级标题-比二级标题小一号" class="headerlink" title="三级标题(比二级标题小一号)"></a>三级标题(比二级标题小一号)</h3><h4 id="四级标题-比三级标题小一号"><a href="#四级标题-比三级标题小一号" class="headerlink" title="四级标题(比三级标题小一号)"></a>四级标题(比三级标题小一号)</h4><h5 id="五级标题-比四级标题小一号"><a href="#五级标题-比四级标题小一号" class="headerlink" title="五级标题(比四级标题小一号)"></a>五级标题(比四级标题小一号)</h5><h6 id="六级标题-比五级标题小一号"><a href="#六级标题-比五级标题小一号" class="headerlink" title="六级标题(比五级标题小一号)"></a>六级标题(比五级标题小一号)</h6><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 一级标题(最大字号)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 二级标题(比一级标题小一号)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">### 三级标题(比二级标题小一号)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#### 四级标题(比三级标题小一号)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">##### 五级标题(比四级标题小一号)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">###### 六级标题(比五级标题小一号)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>代码高亮<br><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><code>文本突出</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`文本突出`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分割线</p><hr><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>图片插入</p><p><img src="http://img06.tooopen.com/images/20180603/tooopen_sy_241631515411.jpg" alt="风景"><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![风景](http://img06.tooopen.com/images/20180603/tooopen_sy_241631515411.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
